{"word":"συλλογισμός","slug":"συλλογισμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n98213\" key=\"sullogismo/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">συλλογ-ισμός</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <sense id=\"n98213.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">computation, calculation</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατὰ τοὺς τῶν πατέρων ς</foreign>. according to the (military) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ratings</tr_> of their fathers, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:17:94\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.94</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατὰ τὸν ς. τοῦ κοινοῦ πολέμου ἔχειν τὰ κτήματα</foreign> shall have the property according to the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">assessment</tr_> of . . , <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">364.38</biblScope> </bibl> (Ephesus, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B.C.</date>). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n98213.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ratiocination, reasoning</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg050:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Decent.\">Decent.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:186d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">186d</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg030:656a:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PA\">PA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">656a27</biblScope></bibl>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n98213.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">plan, scheme</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">συνελογίσατο . . συλλογισμὸν Ἰβηρικὸν καὶ βαρβαρικόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:98:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.98.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ τῇ τύχῃ πιστεύων ἀλλὰ τοῖς ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:7:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.7.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n98213.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">putting together of observed facts</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg005.perseus-grc1:412a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cra.\">Cra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">412a</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. ἐστιν ὅτι τοῦτο ἐκεῖνο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg038.perseus-grc1:1371b:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1371b9</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inference</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1595.tlg472:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sign.\">Sign.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14</biblScope></bibl>, al. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n98213.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in the Logic of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author></bibl>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a syllogism</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">deductive argument</tr_>, defined provisionally as an argument in which, certain things being posited, something different from them necessarily follows, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:24b:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ APr.\">APr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24b18</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:47a:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">47a34</biblScope></bibl>, al.; of several kinds, e.g. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἀποδεικτικὸς ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:74b:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ APo.\">APo.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">74b11</biblScope> </bibl>; <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">διαλεκτικὸς ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg044:100a:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Top.\">Top.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">100a22</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐριστικὸς ς</foreign>. ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg044:b24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">b24</biblScope> </bibl>; sts. opposed to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπαγωγή</foreign> (q.v.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἐξ ἐπαγωγῆς ς</foreign>. the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">syllogism</tr_> which springs out of induction, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:68b:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ APr.\">APr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">68b15</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ ἐνθύμημα ς. τις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg038.perseus-grc1:1355a:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1355a8</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n98213.5\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> Rhet., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inference from written to unwritten law</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0592.tlg002:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hermog.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Stat.\">Stat.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</biblScope></bibl>, al. (cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4017.tlg004:2:198\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Syrian.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">in Hermog.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.198</biblScope> </bibl> R., al.): pl., ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4017.tlg004:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}